Barroso Confident That Crisis-Response Deal Reachable, EU Says

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-10-21T10:30:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/barroso-confident-that-crisis-response-deal-reachable-eu-says.html
The European Union said European
Commission President  Jose Barroso  is “confident that a deal can
be reached” on a comprehensive response to the debt crisis.  Barroso reiterated that a “decisive response is
essential” at the Oct. 23 summit of national leaders to restore
market confidence, Pia Ahrenkilde-Hansen, a spokeswoman for the
commission, told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Stearns in Brussels at 
 jstearns2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  